## Dynamic Programming Optimizations

### Advanced DP Techniques
- **Convex Hull Trick** (`dynamic_programming/optimizations/convex_hull_trick.cpp`)
  - Optimize DP with linear functions
  - Also known as Li Chao Tree or CHT
  - O(n log n) or O(n) amortized

- **Divide and Conquer DP** (`dynamic_programming/optimizations/divide_conquer_dp.cpp`)
  - Optimizes range DP problems
  - O(n * m * log m) instead of O(n * m^2)
  - Used for optimal BST and similar problems

- **Knuth Optimization** (`dynamic_programming/optimizations/knuth_optimization.cpp`)
  - Optimizes DP with quadrangle inequality
  - O(n^2) instead of O(n^3)
  - Used for matrix chain multiplication

